description:
This is a training class for those who want to learn how to develop a multiple linear regression model through hands-on practice.

In this 2-hr training course, I will walk you through a 6-step modeling process step-by-step. Together, we will solve a real-world modeling project using SAS software. I will provide extensive demo on SAS coding, running codes, and explaining outputs for each step. All SAS codes and modeling data will be made available to you as well.

The goal for this training is for you to be able to develop a professional-level linear regression model independently.
title: Linear Regression Modeling in 6 Easy Steps
